{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSSValueList","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValueList","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document_Object_Model\">Document Object Model</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValueList\"><code>CSSValueList</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>属性</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValueList/length\"><code>length</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSValueList/item\"><code>item()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for DOM</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>The <code><strong>CSSValueList</strong></code> 接口继承自 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValue\"><code>CSSValue</code></a> 接口，提供一个经过排序的 CSS 值的抽象集合。</p>\n\n<p>一些属性允许在它们的语法中使用空的列表。这时，these properties take the <code>none</code> identifier. So, an empty list means that the property has the value <code>none</code>.</p>\n\n<p>The items in the <code>CSSValueList</code> are accessible via an integral index, starting from 0.</p>\n\n<p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>从它的父接口 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValue\"><code>CSSValue</code></a> 继承属性。</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"cssvaluelist.length\"><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValueList/length\"><code>CSSValueList.length</code></a>&nbsp;<span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></dt>\n <dd>一个 <code>unsigned long</code> 数值，表示此列表中 <code>CSSValues</code> 的个数。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"cssvaluelist.item_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSValueList/item\"><code>CSSValueList.item()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>This method is used to retrieve a <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValue\"><code>CSSValue</code></a> by ordinal index. The order in this collection represents the order of the values in the CSS style property. If index is greater than or equal to the number of values in the list, this returns <code>null</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">备注</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/DOM-Level-2-Style/css.html#CSS-CSSValuesList\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Document Object Model (DOM) Level 2 Style Specification<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">CSSValuesList</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-obsolete\">Obsolete</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSValueList","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValueList/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\">\n\n\n<p></p><p></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参见","title":"参见","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSPrimitiveValue\"><code>CSSPrimitiveValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValue\"><code>CSSValue</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"参见","id":"参见"}],"summary":"The CSSValueList 接口继承自 CSSValue 接口，提供一个经过排序的 CSS 值的抽象集合。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CSSValueList","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CSSValueList","locale":"fr","native":"Français"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/cssvaluelist","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/cssvaluelist/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/CSSValueList","title":"CSSValueList"}],"pageTitle":"CSSValueList - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}